sses several of the most important problems raised by the work.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 4aAncient History & Classical Studies. 4aBiography & Autobiography. 4aPhilosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / Medieval.2bisacsh1 aLerner, Ralph.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Archive Pre-2000z978311053617140uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978080147165040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780801471650423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780801471650.jpg  a978-3-11-053617-1  Cornell University Press Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK